description: A natural person who is a resident of a State within the United States of America.
A group of Consumers who cohabitate with one another at the same residential address and share use of common devices or services.
An individual who is an employee of, director of, officer of, medical staff member of, or independent contractor of a business
Business-to-business; individuals who interact with a business purely in a commercial capacity
A Consumer under the age of 15
A Consumer under the age of 13
A Consumer between the ages of 13-15
